  "response_text": "A red compact SUV travels along a winding two-lane mountain road, seen small against a broad landscape of dark evergreen forest and layered blue-green mountains. The road curves through the trees, with pale sunlight breaking over the ridge and a hazy glow across the valley. The setting shifts deeper into the mountains: steep forested slopes frame a road beneath a dramatic peak partly wrapped in low cloud.\n\nThe red SUV then appears close up, its wheels spinning fast over rough ground. Mud, gravel, and dust kick up around the tires as it leaves smooth pavement for a rocky dirt track. The rear and side of the vehicle flash past, showing its glossy red paint, dark tinted windows, silver trim, and athletic, rounded body shape. Fine-print legal text appears very small along the bottom during these driving scenes. From a wider view, the SUV climbs a dirt path through open green mountainside, trailing a plume of pale dust behind it.\n\nThe vehicle continues up the slope through a mix of forest shadow and bright open grass. Its rear quarter is visible, with the back window and taillights partly obscured by dust clouds rising from the road. The scene opens to a sweeping aerial-like view of a high mountain valley: green ridges, scattered rocks, winding tracks, and towering cliffs under clouds. The red SUV is then shown from the front and side as it charges along a narrow forest road, headlights lit, dust streaming behind it.\n\nA brief close-up introduces a wild owl perched in the forest. Its face fills the view, with mottled gray-and-brown feathers, pointed ear tufts, and intense golden eyes looking straight ahead. The SUV splashes through a wet, muddy stretch, sending water and mud outward in a heavy spray. The red hood and front lights push through the splash, then the rear badge comes into focus under streaks of water and foam: chrome letters spell “Sportage” across the red tailgate.\n\nThe SUV keeps plowing through water and brush, the front grille and headlights partly hidden by white spray. It emerges back onto rocky mountain terrain, driving across a rough hillside dotted with stones, shrubs, and boulders. From farther away, the red vehicle moves left to right along a dusty track, leaving a long beige trail behind it. Closer again, the front end tilts on uneven ground, showing the black Kia grille, bright headlamps, silver lower bumper trim, and large alloy wheels biting into the dirt.\n\nSeveral close views highlight the wheels and drivetrain details. A Kia logo is visible at the center of a black-and-silver alloy wheel as it rotates through dust. On the red front fender, a small chrome “AWD” badge is shown beside the wheel arch, identifying the all-wheel-drive feature. The SUV then drives across a rocky ridge under a bright sky, with distant blue mountains in the background and dust rolling up from the rear tires. The front of the vehicle approaches steadily, its headlights on and grille centered, before the view drops to the spinning wheel grinding over gravel and throwing up dust.\n\nInside the SUV, an adult driver is seen from behind at the wheel. The driver has short dark hair and wears a dark jacket. Both hands are near the steering wheel while the vehicle faces a mountainous view through the windshield. A dashboard screen glows in the center console, and the rearview mirror hangs above. Windshield wipers sweep across the glass as the road and mountains remain visible ahead.\n\nThe commercial ends with the red Kia Sportage parked on a rocky grassy overlook among tall evergreen trees, mountains layered in the distance beneath a partly cloudy sky. The SUV is shown in profile and three-quarter front view, clean and glossy after the action, standing still on the ridge. Large white on-screen text across the lower center reads, “10-YEAR / 100,000-MILE WARRANTY,” with a thin line of much smaller legal text beneath it.",
